rComments: Professor Adleman is amazing and cares so much for his students. If you meet him during his office hours he is always super friendly and helpful. This course has a lot of readings, but he explains it so well during lecture that you will learn a lot! Totally recommend to all that wants to learn more about rhetoric.
Amazing Professor, learned so much more than just what the class was about! He changed my mind about what to major in! So glad he's at UofT
